Two, I’m making a new skilling area and Im trying to add a fishing spot on water but the thing is none of the fishing spots are like the ones I have. Where would I go to get the ones I have?[/quote]
ctrl + f Item id, when you see the case for the starter, then edit it.
or if you don’t know the item id’s log in as a new user with the starter, log out, quit the server, and look in the new character’s savefiles

do you do ::starter or just login with the starter, either way it’s in client.java
